{"tid":357972,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"［Ballislife］港島籃球發燒友","createTime":"2017-08-13T11:25:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-16T18:37:34.000Z","uid":132554,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"351e2b73488f034c7c6368928a3ad7a6add35aeb","tid":357972,"uid":132554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T11:25:28.000Z","msg":"有無比賽時射極都攞唔到手感<br />\n有無覺得自己個人技術提升得好慢<br />\n有無諗過練但係無伴 或者係唔識得去點練<br />\n有無位置自己一直想打 但因為各種原因/球隊需要而被人強迫打一個自己又唔熟悉 又唔鐘意既位置<br />\n<br />\n早兩三年前既off season, 我睇到youtube愈黎愈多球星/球員既summer workout. 同Drew League 一樣球員想一直保持狀態/手感既, 但summer workout 更似係球員想係黎緊既一季有更大突破<br />\n<br />\n當中既workout多數環繞既都係, 個人技術同唔同方位/方式既射波同身體協調<br />\n<br />\n係香港 唔似人地美國 夏天日日太陽<br />\n雨天 無波打 室內 又難book<br />\n好啦 無雨/有場, 又無腳<br />\n<br />\n有興趣既留個TG大家交流下<br />\n最終既目標係可以group 一班巴打, 每個星期都去提升自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一齊練下 一齊進步"},{"pid":"f5e806e74e520f51ec83c4f1c548b43f106ff887","tid":357972,"uid":132554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T11:58:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46009df5b623042c47ddf70b9b9c5b2a0eb98c37","tid":357972,"uid":132554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T14:15:43.000Z","msg":"做乜Q野負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc7b1812b24459f3cf28c1b9ba21401e6657422b","tid":357972,"uid":58367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T18:20:49.000Z","msg":"巴打TG開個group吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12f24247650af6805cf4b8c699bf7a48368ec89a","tid":357972,"uid":130118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T18:37:34.000Z","msg":"玩具"}]}